{"id":10289,"date":"2024-01-10T13:30:21","date_gmt":"2020-06-10T08:00:21","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=10289"},"modified":"2023-09-01T19:58:07","modified_gmt":"2023-09-01T14:28:07","slug":"modern-wooden-staircase-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/modern-wooden-staircase-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Step It Up With These Eight Elegant Modern Wooden Staircase Design Ideas"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Give your modern home one of these stunning modern wooden staircase designs it deserves<\/em>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are few things as timeless as a classic staircase within a house. With a modern home comes the responsibility of designing a staircase that is not just functional but is stylish too! There is so much that you can do with a flight of stairs in interior design! Take a look at these modern wooden staircase designs that connect different levels of your home and make your space look lavish too.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Floating Wooden Staircase<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the simplest ways to combine classic and modern style is a floating staircase. It is a great way to strike a perfect balance between the two. A modern staircase design like this one is minimal and fits well in most modern homes. Floating wooden staircases are a practical way to enhance the look of your modern home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130254\/floating-wooden-staircase.jpg\" alt=\"Floating wooden staircase design in classic and modern style for striking a perfect balance \" class=\"wp-image-10291\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130254\/floating-wooden-staircase.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130254\/floating-wooden-staircase-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130254\/floating-wooden-staircase-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130254\/floating-wooden-staircase-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Classic Wooden Staircase<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you like yourself a no-nonsense, sturdy wooden staircase design then this one&#8217;s for you! A classic wooden staircase like this one works beautifully with almost all <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">modern interior designs<\/a>. This one works especially well when complemented with a matching classic design for the rest of the space. This modern staircase design with a combination of wooden and glass railings adds an understated air of elegance to this home designed in classic neutrals.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130155\/classic-wooden-staircase.jpg\" alt=\"Classic wooden staircase design with a combination of wooden and glass railings\" class=\"wp-image-10290\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130155\/classic-wooden-staircase.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130155\/classic-wooden-staircase-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130155\/classic-wooden-staircase-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130155\/classic-wooden-staircase-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Instagrammable modular home interiors at affordable prices\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/26111723\/Instagrammable-modular-home-interiors-at-affordable-prices-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Circular Wooden Staircase<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Each one of us has enjoyed zooming down one of these spiralling staircase designs at least once in our lives! If a regular staircase is too mainstream for your liking, give your home interiors a fun, modern twist with a circular wooden staircase design like this one.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130400\/modern-staircase-design-with-circular-wooden-staircase.jpg\" alt=\"Modern staircase design in a circular shape to give your home interiors a fun\" class=\"wp-image-10292\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130400\/modern-staircase-design-with-circular-wooden-staircase.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130400\/modern-staircase-design-with-circular-wooden-staircase-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130400\/modern-staircase-design-with-circular-wooden-staircase-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130400\/modern-staircase-design-with-circular-wooden-staircase-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Modern Stairway To Heaven<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We think this chic wooden staircase design is perfect for a modern duplex apartment! Extremely functional and extremely precise in size, this wooden staircase elevates the look of this modern home effortlessly. The warm tones of this wooden staircase work well with the wooden flooring and cosy interiors and helps in keeping the look minimal yet stylish.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130936\/wooden-staircase-with-wooden-flooring-cosy-interiors.jpg\" alt=\"Modern wooden staircase with wooden flooring and cosy interiors brings minimal and stylish look\" class=\"wp-image-10298\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130936\/wooden-staircase-with-wooden-flooring-cosy-interiors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130936\/wooden-staircase-with-wooden-flooring-cosy-interiors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130936\/wooden-staircase-with-wooden-flooring-cosy-interiors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130936\/wooden-staircase-with-wooden-flooring-cosy-interiors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Floating Wooden Staircase With A Twist<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A twisted wooden staircase with floating steps and a glass railing is all things modern and cool! If you are aiming for a subtle, elegant look with a wooden staircase for your home then this design is a great way to accomplish just that! The subtle grey and marble interior design for the hallway works well to ensure that the modern staircase design blends well with the overall interiors in this home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130655\/twisted-wooden-staircase-with-floating-steps.jpg\" alt=\"Floating wooden staircase with twist which has glass railing for a modern and cool vibe\" class=\"wp-image-10295\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130655\/twisted-wooden-staircase-with-floating-steps.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130655\/twisted-wooden-staircase-with-floating-steps-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130655\/twisted-wooden-staircase-with-floating-steps-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130655\/twisted-wooden-staircase-with-floating-steps-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Wooden Staircase That Is Also Practical<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Talk about making the most of a space! Most houses have designated space to build a staircase. How you design one is what makes all the difference. This modern wooden staircase makes great use of free space underneath the stairs to create ample storage for your home. Drawers a great way to utilise this additional space under a modern staircase. Alternatively, you may also build cabinets to make good use of space. Notice how the last step comes with a drawer? You can similarly incorporate drawers into all the steps for added storage.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130456\/modern-wooden-staircase-design-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Modern wooden staircase with storage drawers which makes great use of free space under stairs\" class=\"wp-image-10293\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130456\/modern-wooden-staircase-design-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130456\/modern-wooden-staircase-design-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130456\/modern-wooden-staircase-design-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130456\/modern-wooden-staircase-design-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Wooden Staircase With An Elegant Railing<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This wooden staircase looks even better because of the elegant metal railing it has been designed with. This staircase in this image here is of a large luxurious home and the detailing on the railing adds to the luxury of this space. With such railings, you may opt for a variety of elegant, fun and even quirky designs, best suited to your style and the overall interior design of your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130846\/wooden-staircase-with-elegant-railing.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden staircase with an elegant railing which adds to the luxury look of an indian home\" class=\"wp-image-10297\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130846\/wooden-staircase-with-elegant-railing.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130846\/wooden-staircase-with-elegant-railing-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130846\/wooden-staircase-with-elegant-railing-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130846\/wooden-staircase-with-elegant-railing-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Rustic White Wooden Staircase<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A wooden staircase can also be white! The modern rustic decor of this home allows for ample ways to get creative with the staircase design. This wooden staircase is painted rustic white to bring in some quirk to an otherwise simple design. Footlights along the wall work well with the design and the unusual stone walls and flooring make the overall look of this space stand out like no other.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130605\/rustic-white-wooden-staircase.jpg\" alt=\"Rustic white wooden staircase design with unusual stone walls which makes the area stand out\" class=\"wp-image-10294\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130605\/rustic-white-wooden-staircase.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130605\/rustic-white-wooden-staircase-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130605\/rustic-white-wooden-staircase-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/10130605\/rustic-white-wooden-staircase-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Each one of these flights of stairs has a unique aspect of two about them that makes it perfect fit for modern homes they are designed into. Want to get your homes the perfect modern wooden staircase that you simply cannot have enough of? Take inspiration from one of these cool staircase designs today!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Also Read:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/types-of-staircases\/\">Types Of Staircases You Need To Know<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/staircase-design-ideas-for-indian-homes\/\">9 Staircase Design Ideas for Indian Homes<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/under-stairs-storage-ideas-for-small-spaces\/\">Under Stairs Storage Design Ideas for Small Spaces<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\